  "comment": "\n\nACL 360i is a professional-grade lighting solution. Features 10 and 45 degree frost lens options (included), fast and precise16-bit continuous full 360° pan and tilt rotation, strobe, and selectable dimming curve effects, DMX, RDM (Remote Device Management), KlingNET™ and Art-NET support, 5pin XLR, Locking Power Cable, and RJ45 ethernet in/out connections, (6) button control full color 180° reversible menu display, 110W max power consumption, and a multi-voltage universal auto switching power supply (100-240v).\n",
